data.description: Enjoy this freshly painted spacious four level split floor plan on quiet cul-de-sac that offers immediate possession. Flexible layout with vaulted ceilings and open areas. Lower level den and or guest suite/bedroom four.  Renovated hall bath with custom walk in shower. Spacious eat in kitchen plus a flex room/dining room overlooking roomie family room with gas log fireplace that opens to deck with privacy screening.  Clothes washer and dryer to remain.
